description:
Certified Professional Program - New Building - To construct a new 41-storey mixed-use building consisting of:
- 1st storey - residential lobby and entrance lobby to the worship multi-purpose/educational space with canteen and servery; no commercial cooking is proposed;
- 2nd to 6th storey - worship multipurpose/educational space containing a prayer hall for 274 p, social hall, childminding area used when people are using the other facilities in the podium;
- 6th to 40 storey - 193 social rental housing; and
- 41st storey - roof top amenity deck;
all over a 5-storey below grade parking structure.
STAGE I - EXCAVATION & SHORING
Issued: 26-Jan-2023.
STAGE II - FOUNDATION TO GRADE (STRUCT)
Issued: 10-Nov-2023
